summary: Adds a outside toilet near the main building and adds 2cm of water to the shower so you can use the \"Bath\" Power of the mod \"Private Needs.
descriptionHtml:
?f you want to know exactly what PrivatNeeds is, then please watch the video of my mod.

- Aspen Manor  =>  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/39400//?
- Private Needs  =>  [ Find Private Needs via Google. I couldn\'t say the link for some reason. }
 
And all requirement of these mods.

This mod adds a outside toilet near the main building and adds 2cm of water to the shower so you can use the \"Bath\" Power of the mod \"Private Needs.
